Samuel J. Simon's Biography




			Samuel J. Simon, age 60, was appointed General Counsel in 2002, Executive Vice President in 2005, and Assistant Secretary in 2010, and served as Director from December 2003 to 2013, as Secretary from 2002 to 2010, and in various legal and executive capacities with Infinity former and its affiliates since 1986.
		
Source: Infinity Property and Casualty Corporation on 04/11/2017
		
	

 






